{"tid":2051622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「冒牌」洪瑞珍累235人中毒 《蘋果》直擊無牌廠房揭三文治變壞罪魁","createTime":"2020-06-05T02:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T13:12:32.000Z","uid":25279,"like":193,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"33ff39df1431dbc6e319e488832efc156d1aab6c","tid":2051622,"uid":25279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"被指侵犯台灣「洪瑞珍」商標及有冒牌嫌疑的香港「洪家手作洪瑞珍三明治」，近日因製作的三文治含沙門氏菌連累235名港人中毒，是本港近年最大宗食物中毒事件。《蘋果》記者直擊「洪家手作」位於觀塘的三文治廠房，揭發食物中毒起因有可能是內地雞蛋變壞或有菌，女負責人道歉及指考慮暫時全線停業。記者追查時再發現，食環署原來早於4月23日已發現此食物製造廠無牌營運，但未有嚴厲執法，結果該廠得以非法運作近一個月，其間再爆發食物中毒風波。立法會議員直斥食環署監管不力，認為政府難辭其咎。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200605/63YRRG7GHMQFU5GGR3BPXPDUXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200605%2F63YRRG7GHMQFU5GGR3BPXPDUXI%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5ErccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=86410525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200605%2F63YRRG7GHMQFU5GGR3BPXPDUXI%2F&h=ced84079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200605/63YRRG7GHMQFU5GGR3BPXPDUXI/</a>"},{"pid":"0372e8ee3a6e1f9faf712d2d7b4a06bebc08e831","tid":2051622,"uid":21545,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:29:59.000Z","msg":"買去警署送popo <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9131ea8216282681b33153cba045ce90cb3cf34","tid":2051622,"uid":141151,"like":339,"dislike":4,"score":335,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撐蘋果最好貼link同節錄</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"11333db0a29350848ac6efe0ed04a5db316155d6","tid":2051622,"uid":29423,"like":215,"dislike":3,"score":212,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"貼link 呀<br />\n唔好全文貼呀<br />\n有無睇新規則？"},{"pid":"bbc4e99f51f324cbf779164859ffb7c904c4a21d","tid":2051622,"uid":41317,"like":97,"di